data.description: Great Oaks, One of the most prestigious streets,75,000 upgrade amount to buyer with acceptable offer,4 bedroom 4 full bath 2 half bath, beautiful custom built executive home. Large oversized bonus room to use) as a 5th bedroom suite with sitting area with attached Jack-n-Jill bathroom. Two bedrooms upstairs features loft sitting areas with a spiral stairs access, Grand Vaulted ceilings on 1st floor gives lots of natural light, super sized rooms. Two bathrooms have double vanities and jetted tubs. Master Bedroom on 1st floor with a bathroom suite (steam/shower combo, garden size tub and a private toilet). All bedrooms have a walk-in closets, Open Kitchen, Eat in area, Family room is wired for the home theater system and and speakers. Large Formal dining, All new interior paint, New floors in family room, 3 car garage with extra parking for RV or boats, Owners have been non smokers or pet owners. Location, Location on cul de sac lot wooded with privacy.
